<div class="container">
  <div class="row main-page">
    <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
      <!-- <h1>
        Checkout our Summer App
      </h1> -->
      <%# binding.pry %>
        <% flash.each do |key, value| %>
          <%= content_tag(:div, value, :class => "flash #{key}") %>
          <% if defined?(flush_flash) and flush_flash == true %>
            <% flash.clear %>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>

      <div class="landing-text row">
          Enter your Mobile Number
      </div>

      <div class="row">
          <div class="send-app-link row">
            <%= form_tag send_sms_home_index_path, :id => 'send_sms_form' do -%>
              <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                  <%= text_field_tag 'phone_no', '', maxlength: 10, class: "invalid  num-elem phone-number" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 ">
                  <%= submit_tag "Get App Link", class: "btn secondary submit-number", style: "text-align:center;" %>
              </div>

            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="row-fluid">
              <div class="col-sm-6">
                <a href="#" class="appstr"></a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-6">
                <a href="#" class="playstr"></a>
              </div>
          </div>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-6 hidden-xs">
      <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/andiph.png" class="img-responsive" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row sub-heading">
    <h3 id="how">How it Works</h3>
    <p>
      <b>JustBooks Summer App</b> is specially designed to take care of you and your family’s summer reading requirement.
    </p>
    <p>
      A well curated list of books awaits you with categorization as per age group and genre of books. We’ve made sure there is a book for everyone in the family… well, with just a little extra for your children!
    </p>
    <div class=" row container img-responsive">
      <!--
      https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/wishlist.png
      https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/cart.png
      https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/wallet.png
      https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/repeat.png
       -->
      <div class="col-lg-3"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/wishlist.png" class="how-images" alt="">
        <span class="how-image-text">Browse through our specially curated set of books for the summer and add them to your personal wishlist</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/cart.png" class="how-images" alt="">
        <span class="how-image-text">Place an order. Two Books from your wishlist will be selected and delivered at your doorstep</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/wallet.png" class="how-images" alt="">
        <span class="how-image-text">On your first delivery pay a one-time fee of Rs.1000 valid for 3 months of summer reading</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod.justbooksclc.com/summer_app/repeat.png" class="how-images" alt="">
        <span class="how-image-text">Request for the next set of books. Rent as many times at no additional cost</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>
       Books will be delivered right at your door step.  Pay a subscription fee of just <b>&#8377; 1000 for 3 months</b> of unlimited reading when you receive your first order. And yes, there is no limit of reading, you can rent as many times as you wish within the three month period.

    </p>
    <p class="arial-italic">
      This (limited edition!)service is currently available only across Mumbai.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="row sub-heading">
    <h3 id="about">About us</h3>
    <p>JustBooks clc is India’s largest community library chain with presence across India. The library has 65+ physical stores and operates on an online home delivery mechanism as well. For more information you may visit <a href="">www.justbooksclc.com.</a> </p>
  </div>
</div>